reviewText: Only 2 stars because it wasn't nearly as strenuous as it advertised to be.  A novice would benefit.  However it is excellent seeing a woman of color as the instructor.
I have a few of her videos and they all skip periodically and will not play on my pc. It's frustration because it's a great workout, but when it skips you lose your rhythm.
It's easy to follow although I wasn't aware that it was for advanced Yoga enthusiast.
This is a great workout, but a little too intense for our group of seniors so I sold it at my garage sale.
